@startuml
skinparam participantBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam lifelineStrategy solid

actor "Quản trị viên" as User #Yellow
boundary "CreateTourPage" as UI #Yellow
boundary "AxiosClient" as API #Yellow
control "JwtMiddleware" as MW #Yellow
control "ToursController" as Ctrl #Yellow
control "TourService" as Svc #Yellow
entity "Tour" as TEnt #Yellow
entity "TourType" as TTEnt #Yellow
entity "TourImage" as TIEnt #Yellow
database "PostgreSQL" as DB #Yellow

User -> UI : 1: Mở form tạo tour mới
activate UI
UI -> UI : 1.1: Khởi tạo form với dữ liệu mặc định\n(code tự sinh, itinerary mẫu 3 ngày)
UI -> UI : 1.2: Nhập thông tin tour\n(name, price, duration, description,\nimage, itinerary các ngày)
UI -> API : 1.3: POST /api/Tours\nHeader: Authorization: Bearer {token}\nBody: CreateTourRequest
activate API

API -> API : 1.4: Axios interceptor:\ngắn Bearer token vào header
API -> MW : 1.5: Request qua JwtMiddleware
activate MW
MW -> MW : 1.6: Trích xuất token, ValidateToken
alt 1.7: [Token không hợp lệ]
MW --> API : 1.7.1: Không có User context
API --> Ctrl : chuyển tiếp
Ctrl -> Ctrl : 1.7.2: [Authorize] -> 401
Ctrl --> API : 1.7.3: 401 Unauthorized
API --> UI : 1.7.4: Response 401
UI -> UI : 1.7.5: Chuyển hướng đăng nhập
else 1.8: [Token hợp lệ]
MW -> MW : 1.8.1: Parse userId từ claim
MW -> MW : 1.8.2: HttpContext.Items["User"] = user
MW --> Ctrl : 1.8.3: Chuyển tiếp
deactivate MW

activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Ctrl : 1.9: Parse userId từ\nClaimTypes.NameIdentifier
Ctrl -> Svc : 1.10: CreateAsync(request, userId)
activate Svc

Svc -> Svc : 1.10.1: _mapper.Map<Tour>(request)\n(chuyển CreateTourRequest -> Tour entity)
Svc -> Svc : 1.10.2: tour.CreatedBy = userId\n tour.CreatedAt = UtcNow\n tour.IsActive = true

Svc -> DB : 1.10.3: Tours.AddAsync(tour)
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 1.10.3.1: OK
deactivate DB
Svc -> DB : 1.10.4: SaveChangesAsync()
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 1.10.4.1: OK (Tour đã được tạo với Id)
deactivate DB

Svc -> DB : 1.10.5: Tours.GetQueryable()\n.Include(t => t.TourType)\n.Include(t => t.Images)\n.Include(t => t.Itineraries)\n.FirstOrDefaultAsync(t => t.Id == tour.Id)
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 1.10.5.1: Tour (đầy đủ relations)
deactivate DB
Svc -> Svc : 1.10.6: _mapper.Map<TourResponse>(tour)
Svc --> Ctrl : 1.10.7: ApiResponse<TourResponse>.Ok(\nresult.Data!, "Tour created successfully")
deactivate Svc
Ctrl --> API : 1.11: StatusCode(200)
deactivate Ctrl
API --> UI : 1.12: Response JSON tour mới
deactivate API

UI -> UI : 1.13: Hiển thị thông báo thành công\n(redirect hoặc reset form)
UI --> User : 1.14: "Tour created successfully"
deactivate UI

end

@enduml
